			<b>The Pre-Purchase Evaluation</b>
Alpacas at Lone Ranch assists you in performing a meticulous evaluation prior to considering the purchase of an alpaca. The goal is to help you evaluate whether alpaca-ranching is likely to meet your dreams, not to sell you alpacas.

<br>
			<br>

<b>Additional Information</b>
While seemingly ideal for many, alpaca-ranching is not for everyone. Additional information in the form of brochures, pictures and/or a telephone interview is available. We have organized a comprehensive assessment designed to evaluate whether the ingredients to succeed exist in your situation. 

<br>
			<br>

<b>Free Ranch Tour</b>
A free personalized tour of the ranch is the best form of assessment and it is readily available to you. Your entire family can get a first-hand, up-close look at both the animal and the business sides of operations. Questions specific to your situation can be addressed. 
<br>
